      "description": "A car with grit, character, and the kind of honest presence you notice right away. This one isn\u2019t pretending to be showroom fresh\u2014it\u2019s the sort of machine for someone who appreciates a dependable shape, a lived-in story, and the chance to make it their own. Perfect as a budget-friendly daily, a handy backup, or a rewarding project, it offers real potential at an accessible entry point. If you want something affordable with personality and purpose, this is worth a look.",
