      "description": "Straightforward, budget-friendly transportation with solid value for the price. This vehicle is being offered as an affordable option for someone who wants a low-cost car with usable life left and room to make it their own. A practical opportunity for a handy buyer, commuter, or first-time owner seeking dependable basics at an accessible price. Priced to sell and represented honestly.",
